  "label": "Bruiseglass Lake",
  "description": "Bruiseglass Lake is a broad, cold basin set within Cyrenth Vale’s rift-scarred escarpments, its shoreline broken by ash-silt bars and blackened stone shelves. The water holds a persistent oil-sheen iridescence under the planet’s bruise-hued aurorae, giving the surface a glassy, disquieting luminosity even at noon. Along the margins, abandoned flood-control pylons and corroded intake grates attest to long-standing siege hydrology and rationed infrastructure. Wind off the lake carries a metallic tang and fine ash, settling in pale lines where waves repeatedly scour the shore.",
